headline: A Fresh Look at Darden Restaurants (DRI) Valuation as Momentum Slows
summary: Darden Restaurants (DRI) has caught the attention of traders over the past month as shares have slipped about 2%. Investors have been weighing recent trends in the casual dining space, along with the company’s earnings momentum. See our latest analysis for Darden Restaurants. Darden’s share price hasn’t made big moves recently, and momentum has cooled compared to earlier gains. Despite a sideways trend so far this year, shareholders have still enjoyed a solid 17.4% total return over the last...

headline: Starbucks to Post Q4 Earnings: What's in the Cards for the Stock?
summary: SBUX's Q4 results are likely to reflect progress in its turnaround plan and beverage innovation, partly offset by cost pressures and soft U.S. traffic.
